nykIAW qy bdIAW, Drm rwj dI hzUrI iv`c pVRhIAW jwxgIAW[
Good deeds and bad deeds-the record is read out in the Presence of the Lord of Dharma.
vwcY = prKdw hY, (ilKy hoey) pVHdw hY[ hdUir = Akwl purK dI hzUrI ivc, Akwl purK dy dr 'qy[
Drmrwj Akwl purK dI hzUrI ivc (jIvW dy kIqy hoey) cMgy qy mMdy kMm ivcwrdw hY[

krmI Awpo AwpxI ky nyVY ky dUir ]
Awpo Awpxy AmlW Anuswr keI suAwmI dy nzdIk qy keI duryfy hoxgy[
According to their own actions, some are drawn closer, and some are driven farther away.
krmI = krmW Anuswr[ ky = keI jIv[ nyVY = Akwl purK dy nzdIk[
Awpo Awpxy (iehnW kIqy hoey) krmW dy Anuswr keI jIv Akwl purK dy nyVy ho jWdy hn Aqy Akwl purK qoN dUr ho jWdy hn[

ijnI nwmu iDAwieAw gey mskiq Gwil ]
ijn@hW ny nwm ismirAw hY qy jo krVI Gwl kmw ky qury hn,
Those who have meditated on the Naam, the Name of the Lord, and departed after having worked by the sweat of their brows -
ijnI = ijn@W mnu`KW ny[ qy = auh mnu`K[ iDAwieAw = ismirAw hY[ mskiq = mS`kiq, imhnq, Gwl-kmweI[ Gwil = Gwl ky, sPlI kr ky[
hy nwnk! ijn@W mnu`KW ny Akwl purK dw nwm ismirAw hY, auh AwpxI imhnq sPlI kr gey hn[

nwnk qy muK aujly kyqI CutI nwil ]1]
hy nwnk! aunHhW dy cyhry roSn hoxgy, Aqy AnykW hI aunHhW dy swQ KlwsI pw jwxgy[
O Nanak, their faces are radiant in the Court of the Lord, and many are saved along with them! ||1||
muK aujly = au~jl muK vwly[ kyqI = keI jIv[ CutI = mukq ho geI, mwieAw dy bMdnW qoN rihq ho geI[ nwil = auhnW (gurmuKW) dI sMgq ivc[
(Akwl purK dy dr 'qy) auh au~jl muK vwly hn Aqy (hor BI) keI jIv auhnW dI sMgq ivc (rih ky) ("kUV dI pwil" Fwh ky mwieAw dy bMDnW qoN) Awzwd ho gey hn ]1]
